## Critical Rules

### 1. Barrel Imports Only

```typescript
// CORRECT
import { FeatureService } from '@/domains/{domain}'

// FORBIDDEN - Will fail ESLint
import { FeatureService } from '@/domains/{domain}/features/{feature}/{feature}.service'
```

### 2. Tenant Isolation (Security Critical)

```typescript
// EVERY database query MUST include tenant_id
prisma.table.findMany({
  where: {
    tenant_id: tenantId, // MANDATORY
    ...otherFilters,
  },
})
```

### 3. No Hardcoded Text

```typescript
// WRONG
<Button>Create New Item</Button>

// CORRECT
import { content } from '../../constants'
<Button>{content.actions.create}</Button>
```

### 4. Named Exports Only

```typescript
// CORRECT
export { FeatureView } from './{feature}-view'
export class FeatureService { }

// FORBIDDEN
export default FeatureView  // NEVER
```

### 5. kebab-case Files

```
feature-view.tsx       ✓
feature-service.ts     ✓
FeatureView.tsx        ✗ WRONG
featureService.ts      ✗ WRONG
```

